# UI v2 Migration Checklist

When editing a page component:

- [ ] Uses `ListPagePanel` or v2 `Surface` wrapper
- [ ] Filters use `CatalogFilterBar` (not inline selects)
- [ ] Cards use `CatalogCard` component
- [ ] Loading uses `LoadingSkeleton` with correct variant
- [ ] Empty states use `EmptyState` component
- [ ] Detail pages use `DetailPageShell` + breadcrumbs
- [ ] All strings go through `UI_KEYS` / `useUiTranslation()`
- [ ] No hydration issues (avoid `window` in initial render without guards)
